# Lendra Architecture

## Product Flow

```text
Connect wallet
→ scan wallet through QuickNode
→ calculate Lendra Score
→ show Trust Score and tier
→ simulate borrowing
→ calculate fee and 30% bond
→ join pool waitlist
→ receive Telegram alert when pool goes live
```

## Frontend

- Vite
- React
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS

## Backend

- Fastify backend
- Vercel production deployment
- API routes under `/api/...`

## Database

Supabase stores:

- wallet profiles
- wallet scans
- eligibility checks
- borrow simulations
- pool waitlist intent
- notification events
- X verification events
- partner events
- social credit cards
- Lendra AI / QVAC events
- admin analytics

